OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FEarly patch cloud will largely
OL,6,Fclear westwards to leave a largely
OL,7,Ffine day with plenty of sunny spells.
OL,8,FTemperatures will be near average,
OL,9,Fthough feeling a little cooler at
OL,10,Ftimes due to the onshore breeze,
OL,11,Fespecially in coastal districts.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FLargely clear at first, but
OL,14,Fpatchy low cloud will soon move
OL,15,Fwestwards, bringing mostly cloudy
OL,16,Fconditions towards the coast and
OL,17,Fperhaps further inland by dawn. Winds
OL,18,Ffalling light.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
