OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FPatchy cloud to start, but
OL,6,Fsome sunny spells developing inland
OL,7,Fthrough the morning, with cloudier
OL,8,Fconditions perhaps persisting towards
OL,9,Fthe coast, Feeling cool at times with
OL,10,Fan onshore breeze.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,13,FMainly fine in this period, however
OL,14,Fthe onshore breeze is likely to bring
OL,15,Fin areas of low cloud. Often
OL,16,Feventually brightest in the south and
OL,17,Fwest after cloudy, chilly starts.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
